<h2>Prerequisites</h2>
<p class="{data:php_version}"><strong>PHP Version:</strong> PHP version 5.3 or greater required to run Twist Framework.</p>
<p class="{data:file_permissions}"><strong>Writable:</strong> Twist folder and sub-folders must be writable.</p>
<p class="{data:php_curl}"><strong>cURL:</strong> PHP Module Curl must be installed to enable updates and installations.</p>
<p class="{data:php_mysql}"><strong>MySQL:</strong> PHP Module MySQL must be installed to use all framework features.</p>
<p class="{data:php_zip}"><strong>Zip:</strong> PHP Module Zip must be installed to enable updates and installations.</p>
<p class="{data:php_cookies}"><strong>Cookies:</strong> You must have cookies enabled to login to the framework manager.</p>
